Grachi: La vida es maravillosamente mágica (Volume 2) is the second official soundtrack album of the youth telenovela Grachi. The album was released on April 11, 2012.

01 Grachi (Remix)
02 Magia
03 Amor De Película
04 La Estrella Soy Yo
05 Químika Perfecta
06 Tiburones

09 Lágrimas
10 Somos Las Panteras
11 M.A.P.S
12 Lágrimas (Dance Remix)

Bonus Tracks:
15 Mariposas (128 Kbps)
16 Mágica Obsesión (128 Kbps)

The bonus tracks were exclusive to the live show and were available for digital download via a qr code that came on the physical cds. The songs were available for download through Nickelodeon's website
